{"tid":558993,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊左先發現男朋友好chur","createTime":"2018-02-12T18:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T09:42:39.000Z","uid":76951,"like":0,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ae068c91ebdd650f0ff6979ee976b8a065b9065b","tid":558993,"uid":76951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T18:46:47.000Z","msg":"借fd ac 第一次開post, sor for 1999<br />\n同男朋友一齊咗半個月，上禮拜有晚飲大左<br />\n同佢搞左野<br />\n開頭識佢係一個幾斯文既男仔<br />\n對我又溫柔，慢慢咁我都中意佢<br />\n但係自從搞左野之後，佢好似變左第二個人<br />\n因為同佢住同一間hall，日日有得見面<br />\n晚晚都要搞，有時我話唔想<br />\n佢就好嬲，會唔理我，我話好先理番我<br />\n有時真係好攰，明明訓緊教<br />\n無啦啦整醒人，話要搞<br />\n可唔可以顧下我牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519a853be89a5d0d0b38ca52dd840bbfd5ecc21a","tid":558993,"uid":135390,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T18:47:34.000Z","msg":"牙"},{"pid":"cc82082e6e702728bf5846c2e4629ff6476376fe","tid":558993,"uid":139139,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T18:50:17.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"8438bfa0eaeed9f5ce39dddc3aac101533dbe38e","tid":558993,"uid":4044,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T18:54:47.000Z","msg":"點樣顧你啲牙？"},{"pid":"78e5fcfb7b621421fd8b879b06093f833a8cf1cf","tid":558993,"uid":53794,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8438bfa0eaeed9f5ce39dddc3aac101533dbe38e","tid":558993,"uid":4044,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T18:54:47.000Z","msg":"點樣顧你啲牙？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T18:56:16.000Z","msg":"啲精傷牙"},{"pid":"e67e21c75cf967c5ba90cdc7412ba3631c6c160b","tid":558993,"uid":5521,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T19:02:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">牙你老母臭閪</span></span>"},{"pid":"806fe1419842d75accb3f1757d67a8c723d6de1c","tid":558993,"uid":68963,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T19:33:15.000Z","msg":"射返落佢啲牙度，再用牙刷幫佢將啲